       <p> Welcome! to this webpage about "Responsive Design"created by Jonathan Tong. This webpage will talk about Responsive Design and the raising concerns regarding it</p> 
        <p> What is Responsive Design:
        Responsive design is the process in which to consider when crafting a webpage. So it can be viewed at a good quality on all platforms PCs, tablets, mobile phones etc. According to the web developer John Polacek it is the ability to “make pages look good at any size” (Polacek, 2016).
. </p>

